These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | 7up | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, engineer
1. the social-worker is on the left or right of the engineer##3
2. the engineer is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | social-worker | engineer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | card-games | skydiving |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
